al introgression, or hybridization, between P. medius and flying fox species found in South\u2010East Asia (P. vampyrus and P. hypomelanus), which may help to explain the distribution of Nipah virus strains across the region.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Olival, Kevin J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Latinne, Alice", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Islam, Ariful", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Epstein, Jonathan H.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hersch, Rebecca", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Engstrand, Rachel C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gurley, Emily S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Amato, George", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Luby, Stephen P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Daszak, Peter", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/e6309d97478524aeafeee963f1eb663f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/254416f5593122e9e69d2286726f1ce58f3174ef367d4541357367009da820da", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/U845VE24", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/U845VE24", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/81183c5dd13611e84e113f0fac463b57!/b71074-73538", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "5", "pages": "970-985", "